      <h1>NRI Home Loan</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Invest in your dream property in India with dedicated NRI home loans. Get up to 85% financing with interest rates starting at 8.50% p.a. Special schemes for NRIs in USA, UK, UAE, Singapore, Canada, and other countries. Expert guidance on FEMA compliance and documentation.</p>
