          <h3>Eligibility Criteria</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Indian passport holder residing abroad or PIO/OCI card holder</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum overseas employment or business of 1 year</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum annual income equivalent to ₹10,00,000 or more</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Age between 25 and 60 years at loan maturity</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> CIBIL score of 700+ (based on Indian bureau) or equivalent international credit history</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Valid NRE/NRO bank account in India for EMI payments</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>How to Apply for an NRI Home Loan</h3>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Choose Property</h4>
              <p>Select your property in India — ready possession, under construction, or resale. Ensure it's from an approved builder or has clear title.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Check NRI Eligibility</h4>
              <p>Provide your overseas employment details, income, and property preference. We match you with NRI-focused lenders in seconds.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Submit Documents</h4>
              <p>Upload attested documents including passport, visa, overseas income proof, and power of attorney (if appointing a representative in India).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Remote Processing</h4>
              <p>The entire process is handled remotely — from application to sanction. Visit India only for property registration if required.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Documents Required</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Valid Indian passport with visa pages and overseas residence proof</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Overseas employment contract or business registration proof</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Last 6-12 months salary slips or bank statements (overseas account)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Last 2 years tax returns from country of residence</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Power of Attorney (PoA) in favour of a trusted person in India (notarized and apostilled)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> NRE/NRO bank account statement for the last 6 months</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

